  <!-- GSAP -->
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/gsap.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/ScrollTrigger.min.js"></script>
  <script>
    gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);

    // Header entrance
    gsap.from('header', { y: -20, opacity: 0, duration: 0.5, ease: 'power3.out' });

    // Hero text stagger
    gsap.from('.eyebrow, .hero-title, .lead, .hero-actions, .stats .stat', {
      y: 24, opacity: 0, duration: 0.8, ease: 'power3.out', stagger: 0.12
    });

    // Floating shapes gentle motion
    gsap.to('.showcase img', {scale:1.02, duration:8, yoyo:true, repeat:-1, ease:'sine.inOut'});
    gsap.to('.shape', {y: -18, duration:5, yoyo:true, repeat:-1, ease:'sine.inOut', stagger:0.6});

    // Sections reveal
    document.querySelectorAll('section').forEach((sec, i) => {
      gsap.from(sec.querySelectorAll('.card, .project, .service, .project .thumb, .service h3'), {
        scrollTrigger:{trigger:sec, start:'top 80%'},
        y: 28, opacity: 0, duration:0.7, stagger:0.12, ease:'power3.out'
      });
    });

    // Portfolio items staggered
    gsap.from('.portfolio-grid .project', {
      scrollTrigger:{trigger:'#portfolio', start:'top 75%'},
      y: 26, opacity:0, duration:0.7, stagger:0.09, ease:'power3.out'
    });

    // Simple hover scale for projects
    document.querySelectorAll('.project').forEach(p => {
      p.addEventListener('mouseenter', ()=> gsap.to(p, {scale:1.02, duration:0.22}))
      p.addEventListener('mouseleave', ()=> gsap.to(p, {scale:1, duration:0.22}))
    });

    // Smooth scroll on nav
    document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(a=>{
      a.addEventListener('click', e=>{
        const href = a.getAttribute('href');
        if(href.startsWith('#')){
          e.preventDefault();
          const el = document.querySelector(href);
          if(!el) return;
          gsap.to(window, {scrollTo: el, duration:0.9, ease:'power2.out'});
        }
      })
    });
  </script>
